      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "rationale": "Equivalency of input parameters between the validation context and the COU is addressed qualitatively through the relevance of validation activities assessment. Formal quantitative equivalency scoring is not required at MRL 2 and is deferred to higher model risk level applications."
    }
  ],
