    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 applicability guidance for Class II devices at medium model influence. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions and the relative hemolysis index comparison against the predicate device. The package is accepted for use in the 510(k) submission.",
